Hi <%= @reservation.reserver.name %>,
<br />

<p>This is a receipt for your equipment checkout. </p>

<p>Equipment picked up: <%= @reservation.equipment_model.name%> (<%= @reservation.equipment_object.name %>)</p>
<p>Checkout date: <%= @reservation.checked_out.strftime(" %B %e, %Y at %l:%M%P") %></p>
<p>Due date: <%= @reservation.due_date.strftime("%B %e, %Y") %></p>
<% unless @reservation.notes.nil? %> 
  Notes: <%= markdown(@reservation.notes) %>
<% end %>

<p>As a reminder, overdue equipment will incur a late fee of <%= number_to_currency(@reservation.equipment_model.late_fee) %> per day. </p>

<br />

Sincerely, <br />
<%= @app_configs.department_name %> 
